net.openhft.chronicle.core.threads

Class CleaningThreadLocal<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.ThreadLocal<T>
      • net.openhft.chronicle.core.threads.CleaningThreadLocal<T>

  • public class CleaningThreadLocal<T>
extends ThreadLocal<T>
    This will clean up a resource if the CleaningThread holding it dies.

    Note: this will not clean up the resource if the ThreadLocal itself is discarded.
